content.p: Print RCWs > Title 74 > Chapter 74.09 > Section 74.09.725 74.09.719 << 74.09.725 >> 74.09.730 PDF RCW 74.09.725 Prostate cancer screening. (Effective until June 30, 2027.) The authority shall provide coverage for prostate cancer screening under this chapter, provided that the screening is delivered upon the recommendation of the patient's physician, *advanced registered nurse practitioner, or physician assistant. [ 2011 1st sp.s. c 15 s 46 ; 2006 c 367 s 8 .] NOTES: *Reviser's note: The term "advanced registered nurse practitioner" was changed to "advanced practice registered nurse" by 2024 c 239 s 1, effective June 30, 2027.
